summary:
Correctly known as Cloumer in their native land, an island south of Tamriel they inhabited before the High Elves ransacked and burnt the island to the ground, forcing the sky elves to flee to Tamriel, specifically Skyrim.

*Adds a new playable race, Sky Elf
*Compatible with most mods that i know of
descriptionHtml:
THIS IS MY FIRST EVER MOD SO IT IS NOT PERFECT! 
Please leave suggestions for new mods or updates I could make to this mod :) 

To make the Sky Elf look as it should, change the eyes to "Blind Eyes' and the hair to white style, although you can make the features how you like them. 

Add me on steam @ Crunchy Napkin

Steam Version: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=739099968&searchtext=sky+elf


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


Correctly known as Cloumer in their native land, an island south of Tamriel they inhabited before the High Elves ransacked and burnt the island to the ground, forcing the sky elves to flee to Tamriel, specifically Skyrim. 

*Adds a new playable race, Sky Elf 
*Compatible with most mods that i know of
